    "<p>Historian of ancient and medieval art; the director of the Index of Christian Art from 1942 to 1951.": [],
    "Burke received his AB (1928), MA (1931), and PhD (1932) from Princeton University, completing the final two years of his graduate work under <a href=\"/panofskye\">Erwin Panofsky</a> at the University of Hamburg.": [],
